HOLSTER SHEATH STRAP

Usage: ^gHOLSTER <weapon> <holster>
       SHEATH <weapon> <sheath>^n

This command is used to place a weapon into a holster/sheath, to
prepare it for readying and drawing in combat.

If you have more than one holster sharing a name you can access the
items past the first by using 2.holster, 3.holster etc.

^WSee Also: READY, DRAW^n

